   182	
   183	    Optional env vars:
   184	
   185	    | Env var | Default | Meaning |
   186	    |---------|---------|---------|
   187	    | ``KEEPER_SERVER`` | ``keepersecurity.com`` | Commander server hostname. |
   188	    | ``KEEPER_CONFIG`` | empty | Commander config JSON to warm before login. |
   189	
   190	    Hardening notes:
   191	
   192	    - Values are read once and never logged by the helper.
   193	    - The Commander and ``pyotp`` imports are lazy, so non-Commander
   194	      code paths still import without those packages.
   195	    - The login path sleeps past the edge of a TOTP window before
   196	      sending the code, then uses the shared headless ``_AutoLoginUi``.
   197	
   198	    This helper honours the :class:`LoginHelper` Protocol, so custom
   199	    helpers can re-export ``EnvLoginHelper().load_keeper_creds`` and
   200	    ``.keeper_login`` for a zero-code shim.
