   128	
   129	Follow **[scripts/provision_manual.md](scripts/provision_manual.md)** in order: test users, PAM User + PAM Remote Browser (RBI), shared folder, enterprise role, “request access” record, audit alert + webhook URL. Run Commander from this machine so UIDs and paths stay consistent.
